# Assets Loans And Receivables Non Current Other DRF 300 Amount

## identifier
de9072

## type
float

## definition
This is a balancing item in the list in which it is being used.

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of other receivables as required on DRF_300, classified as non-current in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.NonCurrentOtherDRF300.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
